namespace PizzaTyped

features
	Pizza {abstract}
		mandatory
			Topping
				or
					Salami
					Ham
					Mozzarella
			Size
				alternative
					Normal
					Big
			Dough
				alternative
					Neapolitan
					Sicilian
		optional
			CheesyCrust
			Integer SpicyLevel
constraints
	CheesyCrust => Big
	SpicyLevel >= 1 & SpicyLevel <= 5
